A police officer was shot and injured during an exchange of fire with suspected thugs in Juja, Kiambu on Friday night. Two of the suspected thugs were shot dead after a dramatic chase. The injured officer was hit in the thigh and is out of danger.Police say the incident happened in Juja Farm where the gang had escaped to after a robbery in the town.In June, police killed two suspected thugs, who attempted to snatch a woman's handbag, on Juja Road near Mathare slum.They said the bag and other valuables were recovered.